MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping loads data into gross margin table for Direct LOB, sales category.
MAPPING.NAME: m_OUTLET_GROSS_MARGIN_SALES_DLY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Acts as a safe expression after the source definition
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Acts as a safe expression Before the target definition.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_SAFE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(I_AS_OF_DATE),ABORT('Job failed as there is no valid sltrn_gl_applied_dt from source'),I_AS_OF_DATE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ORDER_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, DTC_ITEM.CUR_TOT_STD_COST_PER_DZ_UNITS as CUR_TOT_STD_COST_PER_DZ_UNITS, DTC_ITEM.ITEMS_PER_PK as ITEMS_PER_PK, 1 as DUMMY FROM DTC_ITEM WHERE DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE='DR-NS'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Fetches the data from the source tables STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_TRANS_SEQ_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SLS_TRANS_TYPE_CD, DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_STYLE)),NULL,'-',LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_STYLE))), DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SZ)),NULL,'--',LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SZ))), DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_COLOR)),NULL,'--',LTRIM(RTRIM(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_COLOR))), STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SALES_QTY, STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SALES_AMT, STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_ITEM_UPC_ID_1_2, STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_ITEM_UPC_ID_11_22, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_GL_APPLIED_DT, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_STORE_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_TRANS_DT, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_REGISTER_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_TRANS_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_ZIP_CODE, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.FBPUR_NUM, STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.FBPUR_IND FROM STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM INNER JOIN STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR ON (STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_TRANS_SEQ_NBR=STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_TRANS_SEQ_NBR AND STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_GL_APPLIED_DT=STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR.SLTRN_GL_APPLIED_DT)
WHERE
(STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_PROCESS_FLAG IS NULL OR STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_PROCESS_FLAG<>'Y' ) AND (STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR .SLTRN_PROCESS_FLAG IS NULL OR STG_DTC_DAILY_TRANS_HDR .SLTRN_PROCESS_FLAG<>'Y') AND STG_DTC_DAILY_LINE_ITEM.SLSLI_SLS_TRANS_TYPE_CD IN('SL','LV')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ltrim(rtrim(Reference.Desc_1)) as Desc_1 FROM Reference with(nolock) WHERE Reference.reference_key ='DTCcoupon' and Reference.reference_sub_key_1= 'Style_num'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on slba_facility to retrieve the item_id where SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE = '--' and SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sld'
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, 1 as DUMMY FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE = '--' AND SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sld'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is performed on the DAY_DIMENSION table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, DTC_ITEM.CUR_TOT_STD_COST_PER_DZ_UNITS as CUR_TOT_STD_COST_PER_DZ_UNITS, DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE)),NULL,'-',LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE))) as STYLE_CDE, DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.SIZE_CDE)),NULL,'--',LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.SIZE_CDE))) as SIZE_CDE, DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.COLOR)),NULL,'--',LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.COLOR))) as COLOR FROM DTC_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CDE = I_STYLE_CDE AND SIZE_CDE = I_SIZE_CDE AND COLOR = I_COLOR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SUM(STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_SLS_DSC_AMT ) AS SLDSC_SLS_DSC_AMT, STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_GL_APPLIED_DT as SLDSC_GL_APPLIED_DT, STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_TRANS_SEQ_NBR as SLDSC_TRANS_SEQ_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR as SLDSC_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR FROM STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT GROUP BY STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_GL_APPLIED_DT, STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_TRANS_SEQ_NBR, STG_DTC_DAILY_DISCOUNT.SLDSC_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SLDSC_GL_APPLIED_DT = I_SLSLI_GL_APPLIED_DT AND SLDSC_TRANS_SEQ_NBR = I_SLSLI_TRANS_SEQ_NBR AND SLDSC_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR = I_SLSLI_SLS_LN_ITEM_NBR

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DTC_ITEM.ITEMS_PER_PK as ITEMS_PER_PK, DECODE(LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE)),NULL,'-',LTRIM(RTRIM(DTC_ITEM.STYLE_CDE))) as STYLE_CDE, FROM DTC_ITEM
